    "Trait counts follow the spec's per-layer LISTS, which the Section 7 art budget confirms; several section-header counts are stale (Sky '14' lists 15, Ship Class '14' lists 16, Condition '9' lists 11, Eyes '15' lists 16, Hat '14 + None' lists 13 + None).",
